tag name|||秦俑本色
tag jj|||《秦俑本色》作为四川省真如视界科技有限公司秦汉三国文化VR系列产品的一个亮点产品，深度还原了秦俑在出土前本身的绚丽色彩，体验者可以自己动手，对秦俑进行颜色的修复，将已经完全氧化的秦俑不同的部位还原处包括中国蓝、中国紫等几种颜色的原色，也可以根据自己的想象和喜好进行上色和创作。  "Qin Terracotta character" as a realm of Sichuan Province Zhenrushijie Technology Co., Ltd. as a highlight of products of the Qin and Han Dynasties and Three Kingdoms culture VR Series, the depth of the Terracotta Warriors and Horses figuring its own brilliant colors before the excavation, the experience can do it yourself, the color terracotta repair , Will have been completely oxidized Terracotta figures different parts of the restoration, including China Blue, China Purple and several other colors of the primary colors can also be based on their own imagination and preferences of color and creation.  在后期版本中将实现对绘画作品的保存功能、通过作品保护密码和来、修改和删除作品。同时设立管理员密码，可以对保存的所有的作品进行删除操作，但是修改只能通过每个作品独有的保护密码进行。当然这些密码也可以任意的被修改。  In later versions will be realized on the preservation of painting works, through the protection of the password and to come, modify and delete works. At the same time set the administrator password, you can delete all the stored works, but the modification can only be protected by the unique password for each work. Of course, these passwords can also be modified.  操作指南 Operating Guide：  通过按压和释放右手柄触控板（thumbstick）进行行走； Walk by pressing and releasing the right handle trackpad（thumbstick）;  通过按压和释放左手柄的Grip键进行UI操作面板的打开和关闭操作；  Open and close the UI panel by pressing and releasing the Grip button on the left handle; 通过按压右手柄的Trigger键进行调色和按钮的点击，并保持按压状态即可进行秦俑的绘制； By pressing the Trigger button on the right handle for toning and button clicks and holding the pressed state to draw the terracotta warriors and horses;
